{"tid":1924601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[[是時候安裝了]] Telegram以外的高保密程度通訊軟件","createTime":"2020-03-13T18:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T20:53:05.000Z","uid":210495,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e4576c8d47a6d9e85c87cdd3496a05150ad9f711","tid":1924601,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:47:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.18hall.com/telegram%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%96%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E9%AB%98%E4%BF%9D%E5%AF%86%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E5%97%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.18hall.com%2Ftelegram%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25B6%25E4%25BB%2596%25E9%25AB%2598%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AF%2586%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A8%258A%25E8%25BB%259F%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%2597%258E%2F&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=0fcd173a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.18hall.com/telegram%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%96%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E9%AB%98%E4%BF%9D%E5%AF%86%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E5%97%8E/</a><br />\n<br />\n隨著即時通信軟件（Instant Messaging，IM）的使用範圍越來越普遍，不少公司或個人用戶均會通過IM傳送重要資料和文件，IM安全的重要性需要不斷提高。繼近兩、三年冒起的Telegram，還有那些值得大家關注的IM？拾捌堂為大家精選3隻私隱保護程度極高的IM，讓大家能放心使用。<br />\n<br />\n一.Signal（前稱TextSecure Private Messenger）<br />\n即時通訊和語音平台最初由Moxie Marlinspike和Trevor Perrin的Whisper Systems創建。連披露「稜鏡計畫」的美國中央情報局前職員史諾登（Edward Snowden）都愛用的Signal，是採用標準流動電話號碼為識別號，並設有點對點加密功能，以確保Signal用戶間的通訊保密。值得注意的是，Signal能防止對方截屏，對經常傳送秘密信息的用戶，這功能相當有吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.18hall.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/%E6%90%9C%E7%8B%97%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20181108184325.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.18hall.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F%25E6%2590%259C%25E7%258B%2597%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE20181108184325.png&h=e9c34932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二.Wire<br />\n由Wire Swiss開發的Wire，強大之處在於支援多平台同步記錄對話。Wire能兼容於iOS、 Android和Linux平台，最多支持128人群聊（Group Chat）的Wire能為用家在不同平台使用的通訊記錄都設置一個獨立的私鑰，解決了傳輸過程中的加密問題，以及多個設備同時登入的難題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.18hall.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/%E6%90%9C%E7%8B%97%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20181108184619-1024x640.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.18hall.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F%25E6%2590%259C%25E7%258B%2597%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE20181108184619-1024x640.png&h=0122a33a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三.Wickr<br />\n在東歐非常流行的Wickr，連國際人權基金會（Human Rights Foundation）CEO Thor Halvorssen及CIA風險投資部門In-Q-Tel等知名用戶都對Wickr的保密性投以信任一票。同樣對每條消息採取點對點加密的Wickr，厲害之處在於從不在Wickr的伺服器上甚至連手機號碼及電子郵件地址的任何數據都不儲存，讓用戶用自己指定的加密散列數（Cryptographic hash function）尋找特定用戶溝通。<br />\n<br />\nWickr現時已發展至擁有Wickr me、Wickr pro及Wickr Enterprise三個版本，用家可按自身的需要選擇不同版本。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.18hall.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/PrivacyBundle-Image-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.18hall.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FPrivacyBundle-Image-2.png&h=f2f04530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除了好玩，不少用戶也開始關注即時通訊軟件保安措施，以上推介的三款即時通訊軟件均有採用點對點加密，代表即使是服務供應商或黑客攔截，也無法破解你的訊息，亦看不見通訊內容。以上三個即時通訊軟件雖然安全程度十足，但輪好玩也未必及得上老大哥Telegram。想知道Telegram的強大之處嗎？立即看Telegram是怎樣令用戶數量5年達2億大關的吧！"},{"pid":"3b9eb10149f50c1a927194dad8ae5b1db859e65f","tid":1924601,"uid":102835,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:51:31.000Z","msg":"Tg channel散料就有用<br />\n私下聯絡都係Wickr好"},{"pid":"f2eea0d5b1c2b90ce71e802eca894fb0b726dfed","tid":1924601,"uid":201605,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:55:04.000Z","msg":"問題係message save過係SSD，del左又未overwrite，班甲甴就復原到。"},{"pid":"4c52cc40c9eb17e31ad6c328ab9278f2a12000d1","tid":1924601,"uid":27008,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:57:48.000Z","msg":"最安全一定係cs1.6用子彈溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0c9c0e1b09c76b6cf9ec076340e7856eafa763","tid":1924601,"uid":79351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T19:02:15.000Z","msg":"買部ps4 屠龍時傾下點合作囉<br />\nmhw 就出新龍"},{"pid":"3dc60fccb3b2989759fac8fccc68f03cc207eeb8","tid":1924601,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b9eb10149f50c1a927194dad8ae5b1db859e65f","tid":1924601,"uid":102835,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:51:31.000Z","msg":"Tg channel散料就有用<br />\n私下聯絡都係Wickr好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T19:11:37.000Z","msg":"Wickr是加密但並非開源<br />\n即係點"},{"pid":"2761a8ba69b3fba984283bfce1b5f87c259f080a","tid":1924601,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"tuiiiiiiiii"},{"pid":"55159b2d3b14efb5f0b56ee846758625ec8c602c","tid":1924601,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc07b51d2c2bfcfb35adad518aa17e20c0c2a00","tid":1924601,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dc60fccb3b2989759fac8fccc68f03cc207eeb8","tid":1924601,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b9eb10149f50c1a927194dad8ae5b1db859e65f","tid":1924601,"uid":102835,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:51:31.000Z","msg":"Tg channel散料就有用<br />\n私下聯絡都係Wickr好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T19:11:37.000Z","msg":"Wickr是加密但並非開源<br />\n即係點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:28:21.000Z","msg":"冇開源:有冇後門/bug 冇人知<br />\n但有開源 大家可以知啲code 有咩問題,少啲後門"},{"pid":"c9ef0c1535b4aa643fe1378ca66400288f01d97b","tid":1924601,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:36:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n係時候諗下轉場"},{"pid":"c29be8e6b22cd823fb0e2682b32987a54dd6c072","tid":1924601,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cc07b51d2c2bfcfb35adad518aa17e20c0c2a00","tid":1924601,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dc60fccb3b2989759fac8fccc68f03cc207eeb8","tid":1924601,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b9eb10149f50c1a927194dad8ae5b1db859e65f","tid":1924601,"uid":102835,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:51:31.000Z","msg":"Tg channel散料就有用<br />\n私下聯絡都係Wickr好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T19:11:37.000Z","msg":"Wickr是加密但並非開源<br />\n即係點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:28:21.000Z","msg":"冇開源:有冇後門/bug 冇人知<br />\n但有開源 大家可以知啲code 有咩問題,少啲後門"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:58:20.000Z","msg":"Wickr wire signal邊隻好啲"},{"pid":"6b1eeb118838aa746938daa4203e41ce7cc1ba14","tid":1924601,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c29be8e6b22cd823fb0e2682b32987a54dd6c072","tid":1924601,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cc07b51d2c2bfcfb35adad518aa17e20c0c2a00","tid":1924601,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dc60fccb3b2989759fac8fccc68f03cc207eeb8","tid":1924601,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T19:11:37.000Z","msg":"Wickr是加密但並非開源<br />\n即係點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:28:21.000Z","msg":"冇開源:有冇後門/bug 冇人知<br />\n但有開源 大家可以知啲code 有咩問題,少啲後門"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:58:20.000Z","msg":"Wickr wire signal邊隻好啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:01:27.000Z","msg":"wickr最安全，同時load嘢send嘢最慢，因為多重加密<br />\nsignal同wire差唔多，但連線方面好過wickr好多"},{"pid":"604512a899dda819b32b16b43b4685dd69a2c33c","tid":1924601,"uid":2129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:44:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1cbdd00ee49c540d2e8ecc530daef38249bea994","tid":1924601,"uid":99420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a05a28f11dc55a29599275988aa5813072c980b","tid":1924601,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ca8167900a5c87a24e5483a7c354f5bc8cc6a2","tid":1924601,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:32:59.000Z","msg":"建議大家轉用Wire<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1498046\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1498046</a><br />\n<br />\n就算用太空卡都會有位置資訊同 imei 嘅問題，因為 Telegram 始終需要用電話號碼登記，所以要用埋另一部電話先相對安全。<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁點解唔轉用Wire？佢係一個比 Telegram 更安全嘅平台，其實 Telegram 群組係<span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span>點對點加密，只有個人對話先可以選擇加密，而 Wire 係所有對話都係加密。而且 Wire 係開源，所以程式碼係公開，可以保證一定冇 backdoor。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最重要係 Wire 唔駛登記電話號碼</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n被美國通緝嘅斯諾登都認為 Wire 係安全同值得推介 (佢曾經係美國 CIA 技術員，有份參與稜鏡計劃監聽美國民眾，最終遭到美國和英國的通緝)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eEYVWmLVkF4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeEYVWmLVkF4&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=c2f7d0b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eEYVWmLVkF4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想詳細知道點解 Wire 比Telegram 更安全可以睇下面條 link，會有更詳細嘅比較：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.securemessagingapps.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.securemessagingapps.com%2F&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=7b42fa67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.securemessagingapps.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係官方介紹:<br />\n<br />\nWire 使用端到端加密保護您的業務及個人之聊天、文件和通話。所有數據均受歐洲隱私法保護。 <br />\n<br />\nWire 結合了強大的端到端加密和出色的用戶體驗，功能強大，助您在團隊中完成工作，聯繫您的朋友和家人。 <br />\n<br />\n它適用於所有主要平台和裝置，因此您的聊天，文件和通話始終保持同步，隨時隨地可掌握最新資訊。 <br />\n<br />\n・<span style=\"color: red;\">端到端加密 - 聊天，通話和文件是加密的</span>，只有參與者持有密鑰才能解鎖對話或文件。 Wire不會存取您的對話。 <br />\n<br />\n・總部設在歐洲 - Wire 遵循嚴格的瑞士數據保護法律，所有服務器均位於德國和愛爾蘭。 <br />\n<br />\n・<span style=\"color: red;\">開源和獨立審查 - Wire 的代碼是100% 開源，並由獨立的安全專家定期審​​查</span>。 <br />\n<br />\n・手機，平板電腦，個人電腦 - 會話和文件始終保持同步，<span style=\"color: red;\">您無需手機號碼即可註冊或登錄</span>。 <br />\n<br />\n・語音和視像通話 - 只需一按即可進行語音或視像會議。 <br />\n<br />\n・安全文件共享 - 從您的設備或如 Dropbox等端雲服務安全地發送任何文件。 <br />\n<br />\n・易於使用 - Wire結合最高的保安標準與出色的用戶體驗。不須培訓即可使用，許多用戶說：「就連我嫲嫲都識點用！」 <br />\n<br />\n・二合為一 - Wire 是第一個允許您使用多個帳戶登錄的安全通訊 App。輕鬆切換於工作及個人對話。 <br />\n<br />\n・多媒體對話 - 語音和視像訊息、GIF、手繪圖和按讚使對話更方便。"},{"pid":"fb1a89337ea394a685292df95bbe38b16ac9cd4a","tid":1924601,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:33:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">Telegram 與 Wire 比較</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好處一：Wire 嘅Group Chat 有加密<br />\nTelegram 嘅group chat係冇加密嘅，意味住其他人係好容易可以截取你嘅資訊。而Wire嘅Group Chat 係有加密。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">十分建議要Group Chat嘅人千萬不要用Telegram，用Wire</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n好處二：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Wire註冊時可以完全匿名</span></strong></span><br />\nTelegram註冊時基本上一定要你提供電話號碼，但Wire係可以俾你用Email去註冊，而用email 註冊嘅時候，你亦<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">可以用一啲「即棄電郵」（Temporary Email）服務去註冊。簡單而言Wire可以避免提供任何個人資料</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n壞處一：Wire冇頻道（Channel）功能<br />\n單向發放消息建議都係用翻Telegram。<br />\n<br />\n壞處二：Wire Android 版冇得鎖APP<br />\n好多人嘅後備機都係Android機，但係目前Wire Android版係冇鎖APP功能，只有IOS有。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@kenlui/社會運動it-第一章-通訊軟件-25ab49bda0dd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40kenlui%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95it-%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0-%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6-25ab49bda0dd&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=0246e3cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@kenlui/社會運動it-第一章-通訊軟件-25ab49bda0dd</a>"},{"pid":"3ee20afc95abe66c459cf984c9fdf934c4766650","tid":1924601,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:34:11.000Z","msg":"用開signal"},{"pid":"ca2a88677225a8bfa896d2f4662fe3e00753e70a","tid":1924601,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:34:16.000Z","msg":"Wire背後的團隊非常強大，由Skype聯合創始人Janus Friis於2014年創立。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">總部設在瑞士的Wire具備全方位信息加密功能</span></span></strong>，即使語音通話，抑或桌面版電腦這些連Telegram都未有全面加密的使用模式也受Wire的加密保護！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Wire另有獨立的安全專家定期審​​查，而且所有伺服器均位於德國和愛爾蘭，並受瑞士數據法保護</span></span></strong>，無論軟件還是硬件配置，均有十足的安全保障！大家不妨在Telegram以外，考慮使用Wire！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.18hall.com/introduce-wire/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.18hall.com%2Fintroduce-wire%2F&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=a2a7362d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.18hall.com/introduce-wire/</a>"},{"pid":"0fe00604823aa3ce62e330a4490b686a6cdcb14a","tid":1924601,"uid":182624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"留名學習"},{"pid":"9ae5935c66ae2d4ae8b8e008fb650935f09f4f0a","tid":1924601,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fe00604823aa3ce62e330a4490b686a6cdcb14a","tid":1924601,"uid":182624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"留名學習"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:08:36.000Z","msg":"用 wire 無得輸"},{"pid":"478a225df5a282e9fae9e898e7f66aa7b2a9865f","tid":1924601,"uid":314415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ac93a38a47800cfe7227a26ceb953f2425c86dff","tid":1924601,"uid":182624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ae5935c66ae2d4ae8b8e008fb650935f09f4f0a","tid":1924601,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fe00604823aa3ce62e330a4490b686a6cdcb14a","tid":1924601,"uid":182624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"留名學習"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:08:36.000Z","msg":"用 wire 無得輸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:22:55.000Z","msg":"但要推廣出去唔容易，叫啲人由whatsapp轉去tg都要靠今次反送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c210afb861da9cef403dd2a89ca0859ee049eb","tid":1924601,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"tuiiiii"},{"pid":"38cb8dfa5c7e9159caaca3bc7178bea22d45c158","tid":1924601,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}